@startuml
title SideHustle BMC Section Edit Sequence

actor Student as User
participant "Client App" as Client
participant "SideHustleController" as SideHustleController
participant "BMCController" as BMCController
participant "BMCService" as BMCService
participant "SideHustleService" as SideHustleService
database "LaunchPad Data Store" as DB

User -> Client: Open SideHustle page
Client -> SideHustleController: GET /launchpad/sidehustles/{sideHustleId}\nAuthorization: Bearer <jwt>
note right of SideHustleController
	JWT is validated before controller handling.
end note
SideHustleController -> DB: read side_hustles row
DB --> SideHustleController: SideHustle details
SideHustleController --> Client: 200 OK + SideHustle JSON

Client -> BMCController: GET /launchpad/sidehustles/{sideHustleId}/bmc
BMCController -> BMCService: getBMC(sideHustleId)
BMCService -> DB: read bmc_sections by side_hustle_id
DB --> BMCService: full BMC record
BMCService --> BMCController: BMCResponse
BMCController --> Client: 200 OK + BMC JSON
Client --> User: Render 9 BMC sections

User -> Client: Edit one BMC section and submit
Client -> BMCController: PATCH /launchpad/sidehustles/{sideHustleId}/bmc\n{section, content}
BMCController -> BMCService: editSection(sideHustleId, section, content, callerId)
BMCService -> SideHustleService: findOrThrow(sideHustleId)
SideHustleService -> DB: read side_hustles row
DB --> SideHustleService: SideHustle owner student_id
SideHustleService --> BMCService: SideHustle entity
BMCService -> BMCService: validate ownership + parse section enum key
BMCService -> DB: update one bmc_sections field
DB --> BMCService: persisted BMC row
BMCService --> BMCController: updated BMCResponse
BMCController --> Client: 200 OK + updated BMC JSON
Client --> User: Show section update confirmation

@enduml